verses.text:
And it shall be, when thou
art come in unto the land which the LORD thy God giveth thee
for an inheritance, and possessest it, and dwellest therein;

When thou hast made an end of tithing all the tithes of thine increase the third year,
which is the year of tithing, and hast given
it unto the Levite, the stranger, the fatherless, and the widow, that they may eat within thy gates, and be filled;
